{"tid":629444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[網上反擊] 英國：美英法網路恐將受到俄國嚴重攻擊","createTime":"2018-04-14T16:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T05:34:59.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3be9f2b1249f65eacfdf743d11a952ca3b041b70","tid":629444,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"2018-04-14 23:25聯合報 記者李京倫╱即時報導<br />\n英國聯合部隊司令部前司令巴倫斯將軍14日在英國泰晤士報撰文指出，美英法聯軍空襲敘利亞，開啟了戰爭的新時代，敘利亞空防嚴密，西方國家的無人機不再能如入無人之境，依靠衛星的通訊方式和全球定位系統（GPS）也不再時時暢通，伊拉克、阿富汗戰爭的打法不再適用。<br />\n<br />\n巴倫斯說，就空襲目標而言，敘利亞的化學武器倉庫、化武製造設施和投放化武的航空器會是首要目標，不過若要收到威懾之效，並防止化武攻擊重演，聯軍也可能空襲動用化武的領袖、指揮所與化武周邊的後勤、機場與防禦設施。準確辨認目標在技術上相當困難，意味著聯軍還須持續空襲一段時日，才能看到顯著的成效，短暫的空襲無法為敘利亞人民消除化武威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴倫斯寫道，聯軍還須考慮的是，這次動武如何能促成敘利亞內戰盡快結束，並為西方與俄國關係重新定調。就後者而言，動武總會引起報復，俄國也不會將報復限於敘利亞境內，如果美、英、法發生網路和社群網站遭受重大攻擊的案件，也不必驚訝，這類風險就是現代衝突的特徵。<br />\n<br />\n最後巴倫斯強調，聯軍在展現政治意志、鼓起道德勇氣，嚇阻敘利亞再次動用化武時，要有處變不驚的心理準備，否則會被認為脆弱不堪，國家安全和繁榮將遭受重大打擊。"},{"pid":"d17ad45a0b987dd830337bcf39a6763ecca49bc2","tid":629444,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86565781cb4f4504c64b4d1e68d9052458978c50","tid":629444,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"同連登仔有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13494ff59a52b533164176453eb1e39755f64c7","tid":629444,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:45:10.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰線招人，意密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeda3c48ccbdd70f2c15e434e44d8321fa9bb54e","tid":629444,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:49:02.000Z","msg":"宜家打超限戰，不對稱武力"},{"pid":"2541e6be96cb6d88785e297471c60501d8047354","tid":629444,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T22:51:20.000Z","msg":"五毛最鐘意話人仔鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053bb0929fecda9a5f6abad56092bf90e04ec58a","tid":629444,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5393ea0284773ee5ee437eb6d6bb0beff2d976e","tid":629444,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa4db2f17612d7ac88ad5064559158cc6c0230d","tid":629444,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔：以俄為師"},{"pid":"45f8bc3c2d268bd0dbfe32065ea61515f0d7d64b","tid":629444,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"串鳩俄佬鍵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d6ce4a6485b78d5703f02ebdecefbb58f16bc2","tid":629444,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3d31b305cdad721bfa973f4977587db6eb67c0","tid":629444,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d6ce4a6485b78d5703f02ebdecefbb58f16bc2","tid":629444,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"俄佬都鍵國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}